subject: Attention: Sir/Madam,
body:
Attention: Sir/Madam,
Compliments of the season.
I am Mr Mohammed Ouedraogo a senior staff of Computer Dept of central
bank of Nigeria.
I decided to contact you because of the prevailing security report
reaching my office and the intense nature of polity in Nigeria.
This is to inform you about the recent plan of federal government of
Nigeria to send your fund to you via diplomatic immunity CASH DELIVERY
SYSTEM valued at $10.6 Million United states dollars only, contact me
for further details.
Regards,
Mr Mohammed Ouedraogo.

subject: Re:    Attention: Sir/Madam,
body:
Hello Mr. Mohammed Ouedraogo,

Thank you for reaching out to me. It's quite interesting to hear about the plan of the federal government of Nigeria. Could you please provide more details about this diplomatic immunity cash delivery system? How does it work exactly?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Howard
